# Dashboard environment template.
# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in. Optional — the Setup Wizard at first
# load can capture the API key interactively instead.

# Jarvis API key — must match JARVIS_API_KEY in backend/.env.
# When present, the dashboard auto-stores it in localStorage on first load
# (see dashboard/src/api.js). Treat this file as a secret; never commit.
# VITE_JARVIS_API_KEY=
